               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160710-46-person372">
                  SAMUEL 
                  BEARD
               <interp inst="t18160710-46-person372" type="surname" value="BEARD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160710-46-person372" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160710-46-person372" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was buying a basket of fish on the morning of the day of the indictment, at <placeName id="t18160710-46-crimeloc230">Billingsgate market</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18160710-46-crimeloc230" type="placeName" value="Billingsgate market"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18160710-46-crimeloc230" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160710-46-off228 t18160710-46-crimeloc230"></join>, and I felt my pocket give a jink. I turned round directly, and saw the prisoner close to me. I went to lay hold of him, and he ran away. I pursued him, and he dropped some of the money in Dark House-lane. I lost two shillings and nine-pence in copper. On examination, I found my pocket was cut. I secured him, and gave him in custody to an officer.</p>

               <p>
            
